<paragraph id="8BAF650A002DC614FF53BC21FD2AAE68" blockId="1.[136,1452,236,468]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">
Etymology. The species is named in honour of Prof. Hengwen Luo for providing the 
<typeStatus id="54ABDBA8002DC614FBDBBC21FB94AE4E" box="[1077,1123,306,330]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">type</typeStatus>
specimens and the information on the biology and immature stages of this new species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BAF650A002DC614FF53BC64FC7EAED0" blockId="1.[136,1452,236,468]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">
